{"word":"G3845 - παραβαίνω - parabaínō - par-ab-ah'-ee-no - Transgress","slug":"G3845","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>parabaínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-ab-ah'-ee-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Transgress"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - parabaino&#x0304;</b> - <i>par-ab-ah'ee-no</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939\">G939</a>; to <i>go contrary to</i>, that is, <i>violate</i> a command: - (by) transgress (-ion)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3847\">G3847</a>, <a href=\"#/G3848\">G3848</a>, <a href=\"#/G5233\">G5233</a>, <a href=\"#/G531\">G531</a>"}]}